Subject: [PATCH] gpu: ipu-v3: pre: fix device node leak in ipu_pre_lookup_by_phandle
Git-commit: c795f3052b60b01e80485fad98c53e5e67d093c9
Patch-mainline: v4.16-rc3
References: bsc#1051510

Before returning, call of_node_put() for the device node returned by
of_parse_phandle().

Fixes: d2a34232580a ("gpu: ipu-v3: add driver for Prefetch Resolve Engine")
